    <section class="eb-quotes eb-quotes--home">
        <div class="eb-quotes__container">
            <div class="eb-quotes__body eb-grid">
                <div class="eb-quotes__media-wrapper">
                    
                        <div class="eb-quotes__image">
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="eb-quotes__content">
                    <h2 class="eb-quotes__title">
                        Quote of the day
                    </h2>
                    <h1 id="eb-home-quotes-quote" class="eb-quotes__quote" data-eb-quotes-quote="We say this is an “energy transition”. Transition is a rather innocuous word. But the scale of this so-called transition is massive, and we will need to get it done over the next two decades or so, which is not a lot of time, when you think about the enormity of the task.">
                        We say this is an “energy transition”. Transition is a rather innocuous word. But the scale of this so-called transition is massive, and we will need to get it done over the next two decades or so, which is not a lot of time, when you think about the enormity of the task.
                    </h1>
                    <div class="eb-quotes__footer">
                        <b>Lawrence Wong</b> – Singapore deputy prime minister, finance minister
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>



    
    
